  {
    "id": "f_csv_4eb28016c7",
    "slug": "i-was-modest-they-accused-me-of-being-crafty-i-became-secretive-i-felt-deeply",
    "texto": "I was modest--they accused me of being crafty: I became secretive. I felt deeply good and evil--nobody caressed me, everybody offended me: I became rancorous. I was gloomy--other children were merry and talkative. I felt myself superior to them--but was considered inferior: I became envious. I was ready to love the whole world--none understood me: and I learned to hate.",
